FS2004 -Flight1 Super80 [Re-Seed on Request]
--------------------------------------------

www.flight1.com/products.asp?product=uas80

Package contains extracted installer and cracked gauge file. 

The official wrapper cannot be unwrapped using any available unwrapper. So, I guess this is your only way to get it working.

This package is untested. I&#039;ve seen it work (looked good) but haven&#039;t flown the aircraft as it does not fall in my sphere of interest.
